      <p> I am the Avanessians Professor of Computer Science at MIT's <a href="http://www.eecs.mit.edu">Electrical Engineering and Computer Science</a> department of the <a href="https://computing.mit.edu/">Schwarzmann College of Computing</a>. I am a member of  <a href="http://www.csail.mit.edu"> CSAIL</a>, and affiliated with <a href="http://lids.mit.edu/">LIDS</a> and <a href="http://www.mit.edu/~orc/">ORC</a>. I am also an investigator in the NSF-funded <a href="https://fodsi.us/index.html">Foundations of Data Science Institute</a>. I am a co-founder and chief scientist of <a href="https://archimedesai.gr/en/">Archimedes AI research center</a>.
